# timbers per-repo skip config — extends the built-in defaults.
# Entry shapes:
#   <pattern>       path skip rule (trailing / = dir prefix, leading * = suffix, else exact)
#   author:<glob>   skip commits by author name/email (filepath.Match glob)
#   msg:<glob>      skip commits by subject line (filepath.Match glob, whole-subject match)

# Release changelog commits are generated by `just release` and touch
# CHANGELOG.md plus regenerated site examples, which we must not path-skip
# globally. Skip them by subject so they do not appear as undocumented work.
msg:chore: changelog for v*
